### 1. Signup — owner banao
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Navish Demo",
  "ownerName": "Suraj",
  "email": "suraj@navish.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "suraj@navish.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Assign task (paste a fresh token from login above, and a valid assigneeId)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <paste-token-here>

{
  "title": "Machine check karo",
  "assigneeId": "<paste-assignee-id-here>",
  "dueAt": "2026-07-11T08:10:00.000Z",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}
